&lt;p&gt;Seismic surveys are subject to a consent procedure, which may require an environmental impact assessment. Email the Environmental Management Team at &lt;a href="emt@decc.gsi.gov.uk"&gt;emt@decc.gsi.gov.uk&lt;/a&gt; for more information.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id="applying-for-a-supplementary-seismic-survey-licence"&gt;Applying for a Supplementary Seismic Survey Licence&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The operator of an onshore production licence (PEDL, EXL, AL, DL, etc) can apply for the adjoining &lt;a rel="external" href="http://og.decc.gov.uk/en/olgs/cms/licences/licensing_guid/types_of_licen/types_of_licen.aspx"&gt;Supplementary Seismic Survey Licence&lt;/a&gt; at any time, using the application form below. The completed form must be accompanied by an A4 map of the area to be licensed. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Contact Ricki Kiff on 0300 068 6042 or at &lt;a href="ricki.kiff@decc.gsi.gov.uk"&gt;ricki.kiff@decc.gsi.gov.uk&lt;/a&gt; for more information.&lt;/p&gt;

