&lt;br&gt;&lt;abbr title="Department of Energy and Climate Change"&gt;DECC&lt;/abbr&gt; Licensing Administration (Energy Development Unit)
&lt;br&gt;Tel: 0300 068 6050
&lt;br&gt;fax: 0300 068 5003 
