&lt;h2 id="charges-on-licences"&gt;Charges on licences&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is common practice for banks lending money to companies to demand a charge on the company’s assets as a form of collateral. Creation of a charge on a Petroleum Act licence is controlled in accordance with the model clauses attached to each licence.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id="the-open-permission-creation-of-security-rights-over-licenses"&gt;The open permission (creation of security rights over licenses)&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Any licensee wishing to create a charge should first consider the terms of the Open Permission (Creation of Security Rights over Licences) – particularly the conditions of use. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;section class="attachment embedded" id="attachment_25211"&gt;&lt;div class="attachment-thumb"&gt;
    &lt;a href="https://assets.digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/15148/openpermchg.pdf" aria-describedby="attachment-25211-accessibility-help" class="thumbnail"&gt;
      &lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/15148/thumbnail_openpermchg.pdf.png"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="attachment-details"&gt;
    &lt;h3 class="title"&gt;&lt;a href="https://assets.digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/15148/openpermchg.pdf" aria-describedby="attachment-25211-accessibility-help"&gt;Open Permission (Creation of Security Rights over Licences)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;p class="metadata"&gt;
      &lt;span class="type"&gt;&lt;abbr title="Portable Document Format"&gt;PDF&lt;/abbr&gt;&lt;/span&gt;,
      &lt;span class="file-size"&gt;227 KB&lt;/span&gt;,
        &lt;span class="page-length"&gt;1 page&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;div class="accessibility-warning js-toggle-accessibility-warning" id="attachment-25211-accessibility-help"&gt;
        &lt;h3&gt;This file may not be accessible.
          &lt;span class="toggler"&gt;Request a different format.&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p class="help-block"&gt;
          To request this document in an alternative format such as braille, audio
          or a different file type please email
          &lt;a href="mailto:govuk-feedback@digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk?body=%0A%0ADetails%20of%20document%20required%3A%0A%0ATitle%3A%20Open%20Permission%20%28Creation%20of%20Security%20Rights%20over%20Licences%29%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20&amp;amp;subject=Request%20for%20%27Open%20Permission%20%28Creation%20of%20Security%20Rights%20over%20Licences%29%27%20in%20an%20alternative%20format"&gt;govuk-feedback@digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk&lt;/a&gt;
