    <title>Fire and rescue bulletin: 28/2012</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The fire and rescue bulletin for December 2012 covers:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;consultation on proposed increases to employee pension contribution rates&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;departmental response to the consultation on amendments to the new Firefighters’ Pension Scheme&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;update on the funding arrangements for localising support for council tax&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;government’s policy statement on business rates retention&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;publication of operational guidance and generic risk assessments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
